  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Accounting Executive / Accountant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location:</strong> CT Hub, 2 Kallang Avenue, Singapore 339407</p><p><strong>About Us:</strong><br />We are a professional accounting firm dedicated to providing high-quality services to our clients. We foster a collaborative and supportive work environment and strongly promote work–life balance.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ol><li><p>Bookkeeping transactions for partial or full sets of multiple clients’ accounts.</p></li><li><p>Prepare management accounts and director statements for year-end filing.</p></li><li><p>Prepare quarterly GST returns.</p></li><li><p>Prepare tax computations and Form C/CS for company income tax.</p></li><li><p>Perform other filings, e.g., IR21, IR8A, GST registration.</p></li><li><p>Perform ACRA filings.</p></li><li><p>Perform any other duties as required.</p></li></ol><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Minimum qualification: LCCI/Diploma in Accounting or equivalent.</p></li><li><p>At least 3 years of relevant working experience.</p></li><li><p>Proficiency in Microsoft Office applications (Word & Excel).</p></li><li><p>Strong sense of responsibility, maturity, self-initiative, proactivity, attention to detail, good interpersonal skills, and ability to work independently.</p></li><li><p>Bilingual proficiency in English and Mandarin to effectively communicate with clients of different language backgrounds.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Working Days: Monday to Friday</p></li><li><p>Working Hours: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM</p></li><li><p>Performance Bonus</p></li><li><p>Career Advancement Opportunities<br /></p><p>AZ HR PTE. LTD.</p><p>EA Licence No : 25C2928</p><p>ZHANG JIE</p><p>Reg No : R25141823</p></li></ul>",
